  ],
  "difficulty": 2.0,
  "summary": "根据 $b_i$ 的特殊性质，推出 $a_i$ 的不等式即可。",
  "link": "https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/CF1811C",
  "link_text": "CF1811C Restore the Array - 洛谷",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": null,
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定一个长度为 $n-1$ 的非负整数数组 $b$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "你需要构造（还原）出一个长度为 $n$ 的非负整数数组 $a$，使得对于任意的 $1 \\le i \\le n-1$，都满足以下条件：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$b_i = \\max(a_i, a_{i+1})$$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果存在多个满足条件的数组 $a$，输出<strong>任意一个</strong>即可。（题目保证对于给定的输入，至少存在一个合法的数组 $a$）。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行包含一个整数 $t$ ($1 \\le t \\le 10^4$)，表示测试数据的组数。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每组测试数据：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第一行包含一个整数 $n$ ($2 \\le n \\le 2 \\times 10^5$)，表示目标数组 $a$ 的长度。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "第二行包含 $n-1$ 个非负整数 $b_1, b_2, \\dots, b_{n-1}$ ($0 \\le b_i \\le 10^9$)，表示数组 $b$ 的元素。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<em>(保证所有测试数据中 $n$ 的总和不超过 $2 \\times 10^5$)</em>",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每组测试数据，输出一行 $n$ 个用空格隔开的非负整数，表示你构造出来的数组 $a$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "11\n5\n3 4 4 5\n4\n2 2 1\n5\n0 0 0 0\n6\n0 3 4 4 3\n2\n10\n4\n3 3 3\n5\n4 2 5 5\n4\n3 3 3\n4\n2 1 0\n3\n4 4\n6\n8 1 3 5 10",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "3 0 4 0 5\n2 2 1 1\n0 0 0 0 0\n0 0 3 4 3 3\n10 10\n3 3 3 1\n4 2 2 5 5\n3 3 3 3\n2 1 0 0\n2 4 4\n8 1 1 3 5 10",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "根据题目的定义，可以发现：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\[\\begin{cases}\nb_i = \\max(a_i, a_{i+1}) \\\\\nb_{i-1} = \\max(a_{i-1}, a_i)\n\\end{cases}\\]",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "观察 $a_i$，可以得出：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\[\\begin{cases}\na_i \\leq b_i \\\\\na_i \\leq b_{i-1}\n\\end{cases}\\]",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "即：\\( a_i \\leq \\min(b_i, b_{i-1}) \\)。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "那么只要符合这一式子的 \\( a_i \\) 都是合法的，这里我们取 \\( a_i = \\min(b_i, b_{i-1}) \\)。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar b = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tint mn = INF;\n\tfa(i, 1, n - 1)cin >> b[i], mn = min(mn, b[i]);\n\tb[0] = b[1], b[n] = b[n - 1];\n\tvar a = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)a[i] = min(b[i], b[i - 1]);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cout << a[i] << ' ';\n\tcout << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
